{"tid":664593,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[求屌醒]好多負能量（重開）","createTime":"2018-05-14T07:53:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-14T10:06:01.000Z","uid":119349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"809b7f42fb993148a31ae4487d95464873b2bf57","tid":664593,"uid":119349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T07:53:20.000Z","msg":"個人好重負能量，發現現實生活好似無人著緊我咁，開始變得「佛系」，對感情，學業都唔想理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 開始不斷打機、訓覺去逃避個世界<br />\n<br />\n其實自己知好多人著緊我、好多朋友，早d溫書會, 考高分d。<br />\n但係就係覺得人地唔係真心對自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，好自卑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，俾打機迷住搞到d嘢一拖再拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我知係自己衰，自己冇用。跪求巴絲屌醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到底點先走得返出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca4a3c2ba503314935c8d32676a106ed3eeaa24c","tid":664593,"uid":119349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T07:55:18.000Z","msg":"求大力d屌<br />\nsor 1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33a75d5ed3e5a62c3391bcc8eac0da4e1faa7d55","tid":664593,"uid":136979,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T07:56:18.000Z","msg":"你起碼有人真係著緊你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我係真係無人著緊我"},{"pid":"96b254e51b8de0f3f36d53af50bc9211231ea9e3","tid":664593,"uid":119349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33a75d5ed3e5a62c3391bcc8eac0da4e1faa7d55","tid":664593,"uid":136979,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T07:56:18.000Z","msg":"你起碼有人真係著緊你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我係真係無人著緊我"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T07:57:22.000Z","msg":"巴打好似仲sad過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=